{"type":"answer","id":200306,"parentType":"question","parentId":20369,"uid":40239,"contents":"1、要避免<a href=\"http://www.so.com/s?q=%E6%B8%A9%E5%B7%AE&amp;ie=utf-8&amp;src=internal_wenda_recommend_textn\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">温差</a>过大，同时也要注意<a href=\"http://www.so.com/s?q=%E5%8F%B6%E5%AD%90&amp;ie=utf-8&amp;src=internal_wenda_recommend_textn\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">叶子</a>不要靠近供暖设备。<br>\n<br>\n2、北方秋冬季节要注意保暖，并且要注意<a href=\"http://www.so.com/s?q=%E5%85%89%E7%85%A7%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4&amp;ie=utf-8&amp;src=internal_wenda_recommend_textn\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">光照时间</a>，一般室温10度左右绿萝就能安全过冬，在<a href=\"http://www.so.com/s?q=%E5%86%AC%E5%AD%A3&amp;ie=utf-8&amp;src=internal_wenda_recommend_textn\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">冬季</a>光照比较不足，要适当的增长光照时间。<br>\n<br>\n3、绿萝的生长过程中对水分的依赖比较大，除了对<a href=\"http://www.so.com/s?q=%E5%9C%9F%E5%A3%A4&amp;ie=utf-8&amp;src=internal_wenda_recommend_textn\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">土壤</a>进行浇水外，还要对<a href=\"http://www.so.com/s?q=%E5%8F%B6%E9%9D%A2&amp;ie=utf-8&amp;src=internal_wenda_recommend_textn\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">叶面</a>进行浇水，尤其在<a href=\"http://www.so.com/s?q=%E5%A4%8F%E5%AD%A3&amp;ie=utf-8&amp;src=internal_wenda_recommend_textn\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">夏季</a>。另外，要每个月浇透一次水。","date":"2020-03-10","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}